query:
WITH
       fe AS (
             INSERT INTO feed_entries (feed_id, entry_id)
             VALUES ($1, $2)
                 ON CONFLICT (feed_id, entry_id) DO NOTHING
          RETURNING id
       )
SELECT id AS "id!"
  FROM fe
 UNION ALL
SELECT id
  FROM feed_entries
 WHERE feed_id = $1
   AND entry_id = $2
